        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Safer Heat Act of 202</strong><b>3</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to establish safety standards for portable heating devices, including a requirement that a device shuts off at a threshold determined hazardous by the commission. The commission is authorized to enforce these standards.</p>]]></text>
